Package: rendezr
Type: Package
Title: Consent-First Random Local Network Conversations for R
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Quentin", family = "Lamboley",
           email = "q.lamboley78@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: A local-area-network, consent-first, peer-to-peer console chat
    for R and RStudio. Each participant explicitly starts a short-lived local
    listener; the package discovers only opted-in peers on the configured private
    IPv4 subnet, selects an available peer at random, and sends messages directly
    between the two local machines. There is no central service, no account, no
    domain, no telemetry, and no network activity at package load time.
